summary: Here is the swamp bbackground I made based on my memory of what swamps look like in pokemon, so expect a mix of several...
body:
Here is the swamp bbackground I made based on my memory of what swamps look like in pokemon, so expect a mix of several different swamps from different game

I did draw this to use as a background for a drawing on my nsfw blog, it ought to be pretty easy to find since it’s on mt blog description

Also lately I’ve actually been enjoying making these backgrounds almost as much as the drawings themselves so if you know of any place or environment in pokemon you’d like to see in my style feel free to hit me up and I might make it in the future
